name: dropbox.com — display more files
description:
Love Dropbox? Hate the crazy-huge new interface? Wish you could see more files and information on your screen? Then this is for you.

Spurred on by a mate of mine whinging about the web interface of Dropbox I knocked this up — and I have to say, he's right! This is much better.

Credits:
Fugue icons by Yusuke Kamiyamane http://p.yusukekamiyamane.com/ (unfortunately, from the Version 3.0 (July 16, 2010) - sorry Yusuke!) with the greyscale ones by me.
